gujarati.context:
Here is the translation:

The yogis, yogis remained, saying this muni, doing devotion with love of Lord; 
Day by day very much before, saying this story of Sri Krishna Ji thus.

Here is the translation:

Done evening worship of Ganges there, done Tirth Upavas there; 
Remained many that place Mojar there, got Sri Vaishnavachara there.

Here is the translation:

Kanthe mala tulsiini doy re, joii jan tanama man moy re;
Eve veše Ramānand munire, fare sāry lēvā jijñāsūnī re. 29
